{"title":"ESP32CAM","uid":"32677db4598a540c2b555119b6c942b8","slug":"ESP32CAM","date":"2021-10-14T14:16:52.000Z","updated":"2022-03-31T06:11:37.747Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ESP32CAM.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/esp32cam.jpg"],"content":"<p>ESP32-CAM是安信可最新发布小尺寸的摄像头模组。该模块可以作为最小系统独立工作，尺寸仅为27<em>40.5</em>4.5mm，深度睡眠电流最低达到6mA。<br>ESP32-CAM可广泛应用于各种物联网场合，适用于家庭智能设备、工业无线控制、无线监控、QR无线识别，无线定位系统信号以及其它物联网应用，是物联网应用的理想解决方案。<br>ESP32-CAM采用DIP封装，直接插上底板即可使用，实现产品的快速生产，为客户提供高可靠性的连接方式，方便应用于各种物联网硬件终端场合。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225204943.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225204943\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225239847.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225239847\"></p>\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225315992.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225315992\" style=\"zoom:150%;\" />\n\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225355894.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225355894\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225431044.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225431044\"></p>\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/%E5%BC%95%E8%84%9A%20(2).png\" alt=\"引脚 (2)\" style=\"zoom:150%;\" />\n\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225450167.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225450167\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F.png\" alt=\"注意\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211116225548324.png\" alt=\"image-20211116225548324\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/ESP32-CAM-FTDI-programmer-5V-supply.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"LED1\"><a href=\"#LED1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LED1\"></a>LED1</h1><p>RST按钮旁边有一个板载红色LED。该LED内部连接到GPIO 33。您可以使用此LED指示正在发生的事情。例如，如果连接了Wi-Fi，则LED为红色，反之亦然。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211118175859160.png\" alt=\"image-20211118175859160\"></p>\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/ESP32-CAM-AI-Thinker-Module-Red-LED-built-in.jpg\" alt=\"ESP32-CAM-AI-Thinker-Module-Red-LED-built-in\" style=\"zoom:150%;\" />\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C\" data-language=\"C\"><code class=\"language-C\">void setup() &#123;\n  pinMode(33, OUTPUT);\n  &#x2F;&#x2F;digitalWrite(33, HIGH);&#x2F;&#x2F; 不亮\n  digitalWrite(33, LOW);&#x2F;&#x2F; 亮\n&#125;\n\nvoid loop() &#123;\n\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"FLASH-LED\"><a href=\"#FLASH-LED\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"FLASH LED\"></a>FLASH LED</h1><p>DATA1 /手电筒  GPIO 4</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211118175931265.png\" alt=\"image-20211118175931265\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/esp/image-20211118180134693.png\" alt=\"image-20211118180134693\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-C\" data-language=\"C\"><code class=\"language-C\">\nvoid setup() &#123;\n  pinMode(4, OUTPUT);\n  digitalWrite(4,LOW);&#x2F;&#x2F;不亮\n  &#x2F;&#x2F;digitalWrite(4,HIGH);&#x2F;&#x2F;亮\n&#125;\n\nvoid loop() &#123;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","feature":false,"text":"ESP32-CAM是安信可最新发布小尺寸的摄像头模组。该模块...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":700,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"电子电路","slug":"电子电路","count":5,"path":"api/categories/电子电路.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"单片机","slug":"单片机","count":4,"p